@elonmusk The man who could have retired after PayPal with $180 million and never worked another day instead bet every dollar on rockets and electric cars at the same time. Both nearly went bankrupt in 2008.

Most billionaires buy yachts. This one bought a ticket to Mars and is building the rocket himself.

"True" is the most understated response possible from someone whose to-do list includes the Moon, Mars, and harvesting a percentage of the sun's energy.

